relation: Darrow3 - #04 With our heroes revived and full of fighting spirit, the confrontation with Giygas is finally at hand. You'd almost think this were some sort of final battle or something!
Darrow3 - #05 Plan or no plan, it is far too late. The attempt to distract Giygas meets a quick end as his only interest at this point is Ness and Ness alone.
Darrow3 - #06 In the darkness, a force of light slowly emerges. As it takes shape, a strangely familiar figure suddenly joins the fight.
Darrow3 - #07 With the strength of a thousand men, Teddy restores Ness' fighting spirit. Although he may not be one of the chosen, his encouragement is exactly the power Ness needs.
Darrow3 - #08 Not one to be left behind, Jeff throws his hat into the ring and reveals a trump card of his own.
